Use a statically typed language:

Given a string made of four characters A, K, E, and W, for example 
AKEWEWKAEEKAWWEAK, write a program that will print the number of times each 
letter appears in the string. You are required to use recursion but do not use 
any mutability. Write the program so that if new characters may be present in 
the string then the program will be able to process those without any change.

Provide a script to easily run the program.
